data.title: An autumn week in and around Jenaz
data.meta_description: We spent the last week of October in Haus am Platz in Jenaz. The weather was spectacular and we alternated between architectural discoveries and hikes in the beautiful forests.  Jenaz    is located in the Prättigau, a part of Northern Grisons, following the valley of the Landquart river over 40km between the towns  Landquart    and  Klosters   .
